Class TestSingleColumnValueExcludeFilter

  • public class TestSingleColumnValueExcludeFilter

    Tests for SingleColumnValueExcludeFilter. Because this filter extends SingleColumnValueFilter, only the added functionality is tested. That is, method filterCell(Cell).
